subject: junitdoclet - class X gets rendered to test clase, class Y does not

messageBody:
Having worked out (I think) all the kinks from running junitdoclet as
an external program in my eclipse, I have tried generating some junit
test classes for random class in my application (random just to test
it, eventually I want to do them all with the recursive generation
script).

Many of my classes generate fine.

A few classes however, and I can't determine why one works and one
doesn't, just does do anything.

WHen it works, I get this...
Constructing Javadoc information...
Generating TestSuites and TestCases.
Loading properties from
C:\JUnitDoclet.1.0.2\doc\ide\junitdoclet.properties.
Writing TestCase com.package.ConfigurationControllerTest.

When it doesn't, I get this...
Constructing Javadoc information...
Generating TestSuites and TestCases.

and it stops, no error, no message, and no test class.

thoughts?
